[[div class="bubble"]]

+ Welcome to Legend

----

With the Old Gods is a tale series exploring a world of themes and stories based around Gods and Heros of myth, often in the context of the modern world. These stories range from deep examinations of how these mythic inspirations change and grow over the ages as time and technology marches forward, personal stories about love and growth and finding companionship in the world, and big, bombastic set-piece adventures. 

This is not a canon, but a tale series set within a larger setting. The main plotline of this series is closed to contribution without previous permission, but [[*user DrBleep]] is more than willing to hear out ideas for new pieces. 

The current starting point of the series is On the Rails, though this is not the true starting point of the story. 

[[/div]]
[[/=]]
